query:
UPDATE gemini_cli
                    SET
                        email = COALESCE(?, email),
                        refresh_token = COALESCE(?, refresh_token),
                        access_token = COALESCE(?, access_token),
                        expiry = COALESCE(?, expiry),
                        status = COALESCE(?, status),
                        updated_at = ?
                    WHERE id = ?
